Reviewer Management
API endpoints for admin to manage proposal reviewers



GET
/reviewer-management
Get proposals list for reviewer management


Returns list of proposals with reviewer information for admin management (Admin only)

Parameters
Try it out
Name	Description
search
string
(query)
Search by proposal title or ketua name

search
status
string
(query)
Filter by proposal status

Available values : pending, ditolak, disetujui, revisi


--
tahun
integer
(query)
Filter by year (from pkm_kalender)

2026
has_reviewer
boolean
(query)
Filter by reviewer status (true/false)


--
per_page
integer
(query)
Items per page

Default value : 15

15
