GET
/reviewer-management/available-reviewers
Get available reviewers


Returns list of available reviewers (users with reviewer role) that can be assigned. If proposal_id is provided, excludes reviewers already assigned to that proposal (Admin only)

Parameters
Try it out
Name	Description
proposal_id
integer
(query)
Proposal ID to exclude already assigned reviewers

1
search
string
(query)
Search by reviewer name or email

search
per_page
integer
(query)
Items per page

Default value : 50

50
Responses
Code	Description	Links
200	
Success

Media type

application/json
Controls Accept header.
Example Value
Schema
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "id": 10,
      "name": "Dr. Reviewer Name",
      "email": "reviewer@example.com"
    }
  ],
