POST
/reviewer-management/{proposal}/set-reviewers
Set reviewers for proposal


Assign reviewers to a proposal. This will create penilaian entries for all kriteria for each reviewer (Admin only)

Parameters
Try it out
Name	Description
proposal *
integer
(path)
Proposal ID

proposal
Request body

application/json
Example Value
Schema
